A Little

About Me

I am currently studying towards a Master in Media and Communication at the University of Applied Sciences in Offenburg and also work there part-time as an academic assistant tutoring two classes related to media integration / usage in the web. Above all, I like creative work and I am particularly interested in web design and web programming. The seamless interaction of layouting, styling and programming and the instant visual feedback is what appeals to me the most. In my free time, I like to go hiking, meeting friends and spending time with my family. Besides, I am an active player and board member in a local football club.

On this website I want to share some of my works and life impressions.
